g/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fe9693860e5c863d052f43d4b42b0bb2d76677","tid":1467813,"uid":31655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:44.000Z","msg":"機場真係好有價值<br />\n唔需要日日去<br />\n但一去一定要夠人<br />\n一星期一兩日夠多人就得"},{"pid":"2bc1672f7cc3acab8227b043ea189f5bffc2a608","tid":1467813,"uid":274414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:56.000Z","msg":"同埋今日見到警犬有試水溫式既行動<br />\n等佢地突破埋機場遊客依一個關口<br />\n我諗&hellip; 依場革命正式告終<br />\n起碼現階段我諗唔到和理非仲可以點升級"},{"pid":"9553aaa6c52bd658146864762fbe7b8a6978ef13","tid":1467813,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9ca05a93270ce9bfa9907490d9a1286f69764de0","tid":1467813,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57fe9693860e5c863d052f43d4b42b0bb2d76677","tid":1467813,"uid":31655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:44.000Z","msg":"機場真係好有價值<br />\n唔需要日日去<br />\n但一去一定要夠人<br />\n一星期一兩日夠多人就得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:20.000Z","msg":"主要送貨地係歐美，計返時差，塞星期二至六比較有影響，連續兩日效果更佳"},{"pid":"91e158fb491358ca5341f026534f27d28c7321bb","tid":1467813,"uid":10258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:34.000Z","msg":"今晚機場單野，大家真係要醒 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1468119/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1468119/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"db11808104dda43045414108cde8910aa2b0d342","tid":1467813,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:10:14.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"4e64255692bc4ec1ac1f8aaaf1353b6f5fea2b06","tid":1467813,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:11:54.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"aa827ff6d7d3adef44a5808f191b633c8db6b72c","tid":1467813,"uid":277541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:11:54.000Z","msg":"回應今晚機場事件以及呢兩日黑警新策略：<br />\n示威者做法不完美，但